### Weather API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Get all weather data
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for London
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/london
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for New York
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/new%20york
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for Tokyo
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/tokyo
Accept: application/json

###

### Get weather for non-existent location (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/paris
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all available locations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/locations
Accept: application/json

###

### Test case sensitivity - London with different cases
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/LONDON
Accept: application/json

###

### Test case sensitivity - Mixed case
GET http://localhost:3000/api/weather/ToKyO
Accept: application/json

###

### Frontend route test
GET http://localhost:3000/
Accept: text/html